    <item>
      <title>Worry about many types of ASB is at its lowest level for 20 years</title>
      <link>http://lesscrime.info/post/asb-trends/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Apr 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://lesscrime.info/post/asb-trends/</guid>
      <description>


&lt;p&gt;The Crime Survey for England and Wales asks people every year if they are worried about different types of anti-social behaviour (ASB) in the area where they live. For many types of ASB, in 2022 the percentage of people saying many types of ASB were a very/fairly big problem in their area was at or near its lowest level since records began in 2002.&lt;/p&gt;
